                                      List<ConnectionPortfolioDto> connectionPortfolioDTOs)
        Update the Connection in the DB with information from the dto connection. It creates a ConnectionPowerContainer for the connection with the uncontrolledLoad if available. Also it creats a UdiPowerContainer for all the Udi's.

        period - the period for the connection forecast
        connectionPortfolioDTOs - the connection portfolio
